{"tid":2110682,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【港版國安法】夏千福等9位前美駐港領事聯署 促美國會向港人提供政治庇護","createTime":"2020-07-16T05:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T06:27:48.000Z","uid":13663,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ca228ee00eeebe11a781055316adf34186151253","tid":2110682,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:40:08.000Z","msg":"繼美國總統特朗普簽署《香港自治法案》，宣佈移除美國對香港的特殊待遇後，有報道指，9位前駐港美國總領事和十多位前國務院官員去信美國國會，促請國會向香港人提供政治庇護，更表明支持美國參眾兩會議員提出的《香港安全港法案（Hong Kong Safe Harbor Act）》，聯署人包括前總領事夏千福和唐偉康等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200716/YMEHG3HDAJSDUOGSCJCYGJ7RW4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FYMEHG3HDAJSDUOGSCJCYGJ7RW4%2F&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n3%2BSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=2da96196\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FYMEHG3HDAJSDUOGSCJCYGJ7RW4%2F&h=e70e1191\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200716/YMEHG3HDAJSDUOGSCJCYGJ7RW4/</a><br />\n<br />\n好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本法腐乳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國安法有關條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n實施反制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac7f53754a2947aaa96209969deb960acfe2074","tid":2110682,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:41:27.000Z","msg":"又想同五眼搶港人？"},{"pid":"a6e071765df6ec62789c6f1a396c1abd947ad0ce","tid":2110682,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"4ac7f53754a2947aaa96209969deb960acfe2074","tid":2110682,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:41:27.000Z","msg":"又想同五眼搶港人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:42:04.000Z","msg":"建好咗啲配套歡迎我哋未先？"},{"pid":"3bad5c349127dfd8186a247426a16a358e628616","tid":2110682,"uid":287422